cat << EOF
Services_Weather searches for given locations
and retrieves current
weather data and, dependent on the used service,
also forecasts. Up to
now, GlobalWeather from CapeScience, a XML
service from weather.com
and METAR from noaa.gov are supported. Further
services will get
included, if they become available, have a
usable API and are properly
documented.
EOF

